         <div type="translation">
            <p><choice corresp="#b4"><seg><seg type="prim_transl">Den Allerkennerwunsch werde ich verwirklichen, der darin besteht, wem auch immer Gutes zu tun.</seg><seg type="sec_transl" resp="TI">I will realize the wish of the Omniscient, which consists of doing good for whoever.</seg><bibl><title corresp="ref:schmidtkt1974"/><citedRange>458</citedRange></bibl></seg><seg><seg type="prim_transl">... den Wunsch nach der Allwisserschaft werde ich verwirklichen, der darin besteht, jedermann Gutes zu tun ...</seg><seg type="sec_transl" resp="TI">... the wish for omniscience I will make come true, which consists in doing good to everyone ...</seg><bibl><title corresp="ref:schmidtkt1974"/><citedRange>135</citedRange></bibl></seg></choice></p>
         </div>
